(1, 1, 'Inquiry about available pricing plans and details', 'The user is specifically asking for details regarding the types of plans offered by Quickmake and their associated pricing structures. They requested this information multiple times, asking, \"Mare plan jova che ke tame kya kya types na and su pricing na plan aapo cho ?\" and later followed up with \"Plz give me in detail.\"', 3, 'normal', 'question', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28'),
(2, 1, 'Internal Server Error when adding/fetching technology', 'The user reported a critical technical issue encountered while using the application, specifically stating, \"I get internal server error whole adding technology and fetching.\" This suggests a problem on the backend preventing core functionality related to technology management from executing successfully. This error prevents the user from completing necessary actions within the system.', 1, 'frustrated', 'bug', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28'),
(3, 1, 'General greetings and acknowledgments', 'This group includes general conversational greetings and brief acknowledgments from the user. Messages like \"Hyyy, hello , how are you ?\", \"Hyyy\", \"Hm\", and \"Yes\" indicate initial contact or simple confirmations during the interaction, but do not relate to specific feature requests or bugs.', 4, 'normal', 'question', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28'),
(4, 1, 'User expresses ability to understand technology creation issues', 'The user made a brief statement indicating a breakthrough in understanding a technical aspect of the platform. They stated, \"Okay, Great, now I can fetch the problem in creating technology,\" suggesting they have successfully diagnosed or understood a challenge related to the technology creation process.', 1, 'happy', 'feedback', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28', '2025-12-11 16:29:28'),
(5, 1, 'New User Onboarding Blocked by Existing Email Error', 'Analysis reveals a critical friction point during initial account creation where first-time users are incorrectly flagged as having an existing email address. This registration failure prevents immediate system adoption and requires users to seek immediate resolution guidance. The repeated inquiries regarding next steps suggest an urgent need to review the email validation logic during the signup process to ensure new user acceptance. New users attempting initial registration encountered a critical failure where the system erroneously flagged their provided email address as already in use. This immediate authentication hurdle prevents first-time access and requires immediate investigation into the registration logic or database synchronization. Multiple subsequent inquiries confirmed user uncertainty regarding the next steps to resolve this access denial. This friction significantly impacts the initial user experience.', 2, 'frustrated', 'error', '2025-12-11 19:17:46', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 19:17:46'),
(6, 1, 'High Volume of Password Reset Inquiries', 'A significant cluster of messages indicates users are actively seeking functionality to reset forgotten passwords, suggesting a lack of readily accessible or intuitive password recovery options within the current interface. The repetition of this specific query points toward a potential usability gap in the authentication flow. Prioritizing the implementation or visibility of a clear password reset mechanism is recommended to improve user self-service capabilities.', 3, 'neutral', 'question', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11'),
(7, 1, 'Inquiry Regarding Service Plans and Pricing Structure', 'Users are proactively requesting detailed documentation concerning available subscription tiers, features, and associated pricing models for the Quickmake service. This indicates a clear intent to evaluate the product\'s value proposition and commitment level. Providing transparent and easily accessible pricing information is crucial for converting interested prospects into active users.', 3, 'neutral', 'question', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11'),
(8, 1, 'Critical System Failure During Technology Management Operations', 'Users encountered a severe technical fault, specifically an \'internal server error,\' when attempting core functions related to managing technology within the application. This error occurred during both the addition and retrieval (fetching) of technology data, indicating a backend instability affecting fundamental feature use. Immediate investigation into the server-side processing for technology CRUD operations is warranted to restore service reliability.', 1, 'angry', 'bug', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11'),
(9, 1, 'General System Usage and Initial Orientation Needs', 'A subset of interactions involved general greetings and foundational questions regarding the purpose and initial steps required to utilize the Quickmake application effectively. These messages reflect users entering the system for the first time and requiring basic navigational guidance or an overview of the application\'s scope. Addressing these basic orientation needs supports a smoother initial user experience.', 11, 'neutral', 'question', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11'),
(10, 1, 'Positive Acknowledgment of Successful Feature Operation', 'One interaction indicated successful navigation past a previous difficulty, suggesting the user was able to proceed with a subsequent task after resolving earlier obstacles. This isolated positive confirmation implies that targeted support efforts can lead to immediate user progression and satisfaction.', 1, 'excited', 'praise', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11', '2025-12-11 17:00:11'),
(11, 1, 'User Onboarding Blocked by Existing Email Error and Password Reset Inquiry', 'A significant portion of the initial user interaction focused on difficulties during the registration or login process. Specifically, new users encountered an error indicating their email address was already in use, leading to immediate workflow blockage. Furthermore, users explicitly requested functionality for password recovery, indicating a known gap in the current authentication flow\'s self-service capabilities. This combination suggests initial onboarding friction is high due to both registration validation issues and missing account management tools.', 9, 'frustrated', 'error', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59'),
(12, 1, 'Inquiry Regarding System Capabilities and Pricing Structure', 'Users demonstrated a clear need for fundamental information regarding the application\'s scope and commercial offerings. Several inquiries were made seeking detailed documentation on the types of plans available and associated pricing tiers. This indicates that marketing materials or in-app guidance regarding product features and cost structures are insufficient or not readily accessible to prospective users.', 4, 'neutral', 'question', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59'),
(13, 1, 'Critical Failure During Technology Data Operations', 'Analysis of technical interactions reveals a critical system failure occurring during core application processes. Users reported encountering an \'internal server error\' specifically when attempting to both input new technology data and retrieve existing technology configurations. This points towards a backend instability or database connectivity issue impacting essential data persistence and retrieval functions, requiring immediate investigation.', 2, 'angry', 'error', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59'),
(14, 1, 'General System Introduction and Initial Inquiry', 'Initial user messages centered around general greetings and foundational questions about the application\'s identity and basic operational methods. This baseline activity suggests a small segment of users are in the earliest stages of discovery, seeking context before engaging with deeper features or troubleshooting. These interactions typically carried a neutral or inquisitive tone.', 5, 'neutral', 'question', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59'),
(15, 1, 'Positive Acknowledgment Following Error Resolution', 'Following the reporting of system issues, one user provided positive confirmation that they were subsequently able to identify and address a technical problem on their end, specifically concerning technology creation. While the initial issue was severe, this feedback suggests a successful, albeit self-resolved, path forward for that specific user interaction.', 1, 'excited', 'feedback', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59', '2025-12-11 19:15:59'),
(16, 1, 'New User Onboarding Failure Due to Existing Email Registration', 'Analysis indicates significant friction for first-time users attempting registration, specifically encountering an \'email already used\' error despite being new to the platform. This suggests potential data integrity issues or confusion regarding existing accounts. Subsequent user queries confirm a lack of immediate resolution paths for this specific registration roadblock, leading to user stagnation. Immediate attention is required to resolve this critical onboarding barrier.', 1, 'frustrated', 'error', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42'),
