(18, 1, 'User Inquiry Regarding Subscription Tiers and Pricing Details', 'Users demonstrated a clear need for detailed information concerning available service plans, including feature sets and associated pricing structures. The request for comprehensive details indicates an active pre-purchase evaluation phase. Ensuring transparent and easily accessible documentation regarding subscription options is crucial for maximizing conversion rates.', 2, 'neutral', 'question', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42'),
(19, 1, 'Critical Technical Failure During Technology Management Operations', 'System instability was reported during core application functions related to technology management, specifically during both data addition and retrieval operations. The recurrence of an \'internal server error\' during these critical actions points toward a backend service failure impacting fundamental data processing capabilities. This high-severity error requires immediate technical investigation to restore core system reliability.', 1, 'frustrated', 'error', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42'),
(20, 1, 'General System Inquiry and Initial Engagement', 'A segment of communication consisted of initial greetings, general inquiries about the application\'s purpose, and basic usage instructions. These messages reflect the standard behavior of new users attempting to understand the platform\'s value proposition and operational mechanics. While low in specific detail, this group confirms active exploration of the Quickmake application.', 13, 'neutral', 'question', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42', '2025-12-11 19:16:42'),
