(38, 1, 'General Initial Engagement and System Identification', 'A baseline set of messages represented standard greetings and initial attempts to establish context regarding the identity of the responding entity (e.g., human support vs. AI model). These interactions are typical of the very beginning of a support thread and do not indicate specific functional problems but rather setup necessary for effective communication.', 5, 'normal', 'question', '2025-12-12 14:00:04', '2025-12-12 14:00:04', '2025-12-12 14:00:04'),
