(40, 1, 'Inquiries Regarding Service Plans and Usage Guidance', 'A pattern of initial engagement shows users are actively seeking fundamental information about the platform\'s structure and operation. Specifically, new users require clarification on available subscription tiers or plans associated with the service. Furthermore, there is a clear demand for introductory guidance documentation or tutorials detailing the initial steps for effective platform utilization. Addressing these foundational usage questions promptly will improve the initial user experience and reduce support load.', 3, 'normal', 'question', '2025-12-12 14:00:04', '2025-12-12 14:00:05', '2025-12-12 14:00:05'),
